question.title: How to install Angular CLI?
question.text: I'm new to Angular and I need help installing Angular CLI.

title: Here's how to install Angular CLI
text: You can install Angular CLI using npm. First, make sure you have Node.js installed. Then run the command: npm install -g @angular/cli

question.title: How to deploy an Angular app?
question.text: I want to deploy my Angular app to a production server. Any tips?

title: You can deploy an Angular app using Firebase Hosting
text: Firebase Hosting is a great option for deploying Angular apps. It's easy to set up and provides fast and reliable hosting.
